title: MacBook M1, MacOS 11.6.1 : "cannot be opened because of a problem", symbol not found
body:
# Bug Report

## Description
Status fails to open after copy to Applications on MacBook M1, MacOS 11.6.1 

## Steps to reproduce
Download, copy, click open

#### Expected behavior
Opens

#### Actual behavior
Fails to open with symbol missing. 
```
Dyld Error Message:
  Symbol not found: __ZTTNSt3__114basic_ifstreamIcNS_11char_traitsIcEEEE
  Referenced from: /Applications/Status.app/Contents/MacOS/nim_status_client
  Expected in: /usr/lib/libc++.1.dylib
 in /Applications/Status.app/Contents/MacOS/nim_status_client
```
